		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.navigation-buttons {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
